{
  "stem": "24212.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, my closest friend was a girl by the name of Magda, who lived in the next house where-- where I grew up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her parents took out a piece in the fence and made two little steps, one on each side, so we put commute without going on the street-- dangerous, because every half and hour there was a car, you know.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and that friendship lasted very long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, she visited me in America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We invited her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was in this house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And unfortunately she's no longer with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was my very closest friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Magda Kiss, K-I-S-S.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what about it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, we had lots of languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the whole-- The system is something slightly different than the American system.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what here would be middle school or junior high and high school is packed into one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had no choice in subjects, which I still approve of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what we need in our high schools in the States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had six years of Latin, four years of German, four years of French, no choice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only choice we had was typewriting, and I don't know what else, sort of almost like extracurricular activities.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that was extra in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Otherwise, six days a week, eight to one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And everything prescribed, so that we had a very thorough and good general education.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, I teach American history here at Regis College.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we come to the frontier and frontier literature.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there is more that I did not forget for my high school in Czechoslovakia than these kids ever heard of, which is very sad, very sad.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They don't know American literature.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, public school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was an all girls school, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
